These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, oliveros
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, dancer
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, chess
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, sports
1. the person watching action movies is not to the right of the dancer##8
2. the dancer is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
3. the old-henry-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Cigar      | oliveros     | old-henry      |
| Job          | dancer | coach    |
| Hobby         | chess   | board-games |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | sports      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, azalea
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, software-developer
City: marseilles, hannover
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5
3. the software-developer is not to the right of the librarian##8
4. the person traveling to marseilles is not the person who growsazalea##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk        | iced-tea    |
| Flower       | amaryllis         | azalea |
| Job         | software-developer | librarian   |
| City   | marseilles               | hannover  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, reading
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, oliveros
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, japanese
2 different pets are kept: cat, ferret
1. the australian is in an odd position##4
2. the japanese is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
3. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Hobby   | card-games       | reading |
| Cigar   | montecristo       | oliveros    |
| Nationality   | australian | japanese |
| Pet           | cat        | ferret   |

