.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, sudoku
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, nurse
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: country, jazz
House: ranch-style, gothic-revival
1. the fan of country is somewhere to the right of the nurse##5
2. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the left of the gothic-revival house##8
3. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Hobby         | sudoku | singing  |
| Job           | nurse  | designer |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | country   |
| House     | gothic-revival   | ranch-style |

