.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, scientific
City: prague, rome
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, rock
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
2. the fan of jazz is not to the right of the person traveling to prague##8
3. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
4. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | scientific |
| City   | rome    | prague     |
| Music-Genre         | jazz  | rock    |
| Transport     | scooter     | boat       |

