2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the right of the person playing bridge##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |
| Game        | domino             | bridge     |
| Birthday         | november | december  |
| Pet         | hedgehog           | chinchilla |
| Transport   | train              | snowmobile |

