.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-10::.
House: modern, victorian
City: london, boston
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, software-developer
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, snowmobile
1. the modern house is not to the left of the person traveling to boston##8
2. the person driving the car is the person driving the car##1
3. the victorian house is somewhere to the right of the doctor##5
4. the person driving the car is not to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##8
5. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the left of the victorian house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |         2          |
| House        | modern | victorian            |
| City       | boston | london              |
| Job         | doctor  | software-developer |
| Transport   | car     | snowmobile         |

