1. the cottage house is on the left of the wooden house##1
2. the mexican is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the wooden house is not the person playing monopoly##6
4. the person playing monopoly is not to the right of the wooden house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Game   | monopoly      | bridge |
| Nationality   | mexican    | pakistani   |
| Sport         | volleyball | sailing     |
| House     | cottage | wooden  |

