There 2 different types of food: cabbage, lime
There are 2 different nationalities: spanish, mexican
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, dahlia
1. the mexican is not to the right of the person who growsmarigold##8
2. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
3. the mexican is on the right of the spanish##1
4. the person eating lime is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |
| Beverage      | milk      | sprite  |
| Food          | cabbage   | lime    |
| Nationality   | spanish | mexican |
| Flower           | dahlia       | marigold     |

