There are 2 different nationalities: australian, thai
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, dancing
1. the australian is not to the right of the person eating plum##8
2. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person eating plum##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |
| Food          | plum         | corn    |
| Color           | yellow | blue   |
| Nationality   | australian   | thai    |
| Hobby     | camping         | dancing |

 